  "heading_path": "机械波 / 弦振动的简正模式",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 35,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02060:916b710658f7]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02061:f6fb387f8c1f]]\n\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02062:11000d9b378f]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02063:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n二胡弦两端都被固定，弦长中必须容纳整数个半波长，即 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02064:fae1e34740a4]]。由边界条件和弦上波速公式可得\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02065:aca2e90e83a2]] \n\n弦上的波速为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02066:cec39e01aa76]]。于是基频对应 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02067:2ec462ed7091]]：\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02068:b227c7644a38]] \n更高次谐频为\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02069:fdac970f1715]] \n基频约为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02070:b2b88cbbf3da]]，各次谐频满足 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02071:a238a679fafc]]。谐频是基频的整数倍，是因为弦长里必须塞下整数个半波长。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02072:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}\n",
  "mode": "REWRITE",
