  "read_only_context_after": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02073:8e7148a83e2e]]",
  "read_only_context_before": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02051:ea50df4f6ab5]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02052:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n入射波在 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02053:a6eaf1b0ba56]] 处引起的振动为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02054:d381fc167b80]]，固定端反射要求反射波在端点处为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02055:aec1ab0aa7b0]]。\n反射波沿 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02056:5b3d499a40f8]] 方向传播，因此可写成\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02057:cd513ebc18c2]] \n两列波叠加后\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02058:a4255e53f7f1]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02059:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}",
